item.description: 🌺 Note from the Editor This is me! If you’re looking to contact me, write to me here. 🍇 About # Hobart Phillips is an Australian illustrator and writer living and working in Tasmania. He’s 22 going on 23, and likes machines, midcentury architecture and Tasmania. ⭕ Things I Like: Thunderbirds (1965 series) Austerity Britain Tasmania Showa Japan Italian cars The Series-0 Shinkansen 🚅 Emojis, apparently Snags ❌ Things I Don’t Like:
